_sText:
OK this is kind of a remake of the map de_dunes that was for the 1.4 version of cs.   This is a bit smaller and has no cars.  This should be a good map for lan parties and 32 man games  Me and my buddies have had 6 man matches but thats all.  Its a great map if you dont like snipers because you have a lot of coverage but if you are in the open, you are pretty much doomed to the auto snipers.  

 Enjoy and post back
    Zeke
